sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Chat as Chat UI
    participant API as FastAPI Chat Route
    participant Agent as Agent Orchestrator
    participant Planner as Planner
    participant Tools as ToolRegistry
    participant TopicTool as Topic Tool
    participant TelemetryTool as Telemetry Tool
    participant VectorTool as Vector Search Tool
    participant CausalTool as Causal Graph Tool
    participant LLM as LLM
    participant Synth as Answer Synthesizer

    User->>Chat: Ask telemetry question
    Chat->>API: Submit question
    API->>Agent: Start investigation
    Agent->>Planner: Create plan

    Planner->>Tools: List available tools
    Tools-->>Planner: Tool schemas

    Planner->>TopicTool: Get topic metadata
    TopicTool-->>Planner: Topic context

    Planner->>VectorTool: Search relevant topics
    VectorTool-->>Planner: Semantic matches

    Planner->>TelemetryTool: Query telemetry values
    TelemetryTool-->>Planner: Time-series result

    Planner->>CausalTool: Get causal context
    CausalTool-->>Planner: Causal neighbors

    Planner->>LLM: Build grounded prompt
    LLM-->>Synth: Draft answer
    Synth-->>API: Answer with sources
    API-->>Chat: Final response
    Chat-->>User: Answer + evidence